Comments: This medication works for me better than any other that I have tried in this category. The weight gain is to be expected considering this is a birth control pill. 5 lbs did not make that big of a difference to me.

Side Effects: BTB & cramps starting during second week of pills through day 21; On and off fatigue; Some anxiety_ tension_ mood swings.
Comments: This seems like it should be a great pill.  Good ratio for my age_ but for some reason the pills work differently day to day. I feel good 1 day & not the next.
